data.description: Great wooded setting for this beautiful log home located on over 9 acres. Exterior features wooded back yard, wrap around deck, gazebo, new roof and 16X8X8 enclosure for chickens or dogs! Cape cod design features private 2nd floor master with full bath including separate shower and whirlpool tub,newer lighting and new floors! Entry level features great room with hardwood, floors, soaring ceiling and several sets of patio doors leading to wrap around deck. Nice kitchen with brand new stainless appliance package. Two additional bedrooms with new flooring and  full bath make up the first floor. Laundry is located in full basement that is dry and ready to finish! Newer h2O Tank, furnace and Central air replaced in Sept. Convenient location off Interstate 71 approx. 30 minutes north of Columbu
